<Layout title="Privacy Policy - HiFi Studio & Mobile">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-10 prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

    <p>
      This website collects minimal personal information. We may use cookies,
      Google Analytics, and Google AdSense to improve user experience.
    </p>

    <h2>Google AdSense & Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on
      your visits to our site. Users may opt out of personalized advertising
      by visiting <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads">Google Ads Settings</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Information You Submit</h2>
    <p>
      If you contact us, we may store your name, email, and message. We do not
      sell or share data with third parties.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions: contact@hifistudio.in</p>
  </section>
</Layout>
